Package com.uk.tsl.barcodeconfiguration

This package provides classes to modify the behaviour of the Barcode Scan Engine. Factory default values are specified - in option lists the default is preceded by '*'
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISymbologySetting
    Provides common operations for a symbology setting
